    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce a no-halfway housing zone around schools",
        "additional_details": "My whole life I have lived next door to a halfway house, and I have had many poor experiences. I feel it makes the area feel less safe, and I don\u2019t think children should have to walk through this to get to school.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to introduce a no-halfway housing zone around schools to ensure that students feel safe getting to school.",
